    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/aeqDqQOvFGhfMKTeCS-503mP/Screenshot-2025-01-08-at-13.08.57.png\">Screenshot 2025-01-08 at 13.08.57.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/aeqDqQOvFGhfMKTeCS-503mP/Screenshot-2025-01-08-at-13.08.57.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-01-08 at 13.08.57.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1070x236\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/22008/aeqDqQOvFGhfMKTeCS-503mP/Screenshot-2025-01-08-at-13.08.57.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Added a default index page that redirects to the latest docs, or shows a link if JS is disabled.</p>",
